re;mso-special-format:bullet"><li><i>A little dish from over at Lazard</i>:=
 I=E2=80=99m sorry but I can=E2=80=99t resist a good story in the <i>Financ=
ial Times</i> about Lazard, where I spent six years as a banker back in
