umblebrag: <i>The Last Tycoons </i>was named the <i>FT</i>/Goldman Sachs Bu=
siness Book of the Year in 2007.)<br/><br/>Earlier this week, <b>Joshua Fra=
nklin</b> and <b>Sujeet Indap</b>, two <i>FT </i>journalists=E2=80=94Sujeet=
 once worked at Lazard, too=E2=80=94<u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e=
