=2E4 billion. <br/><br/>I have been roo=
ting for Peter to succeed since he too=
k over from <b>Ken Jacobs</b> last October. Since then, the Lazard stock pr=
ice is up nearly 30 percent. I never thought much of Jacobs as the C.E.O.=
